Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.99,0:57:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,（五条）{\fnMS PGothic}“{\fnMS Gothic}蒼{\fnMS PGothic}”{\fnMS Gothic}！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.99,0:57:10.07,Ruby,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1057,936)}あお
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.67,0:57:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}（五条）遮蔽物なし
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.67,0:57:26.34,Ruby,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1025,936)}しゃへいぶつ
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.38,0:57:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}奇襲はできない　森に隠れたか
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.38,0:57:29.84,Ruby,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(570,936)}きしゅう
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.38,0:57:29.84,Ruby,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1186,936)}かく
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.97,0:57:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,あっ!!
