Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.35,0:57:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}蠅頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.35,0:57:35.64,Ruby,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(928,936)}ようとう
