Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.42,1:25:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMS PGothic}“{\fnMS Gothic}赫{\fnMS PGothic}”{\fnMS Gothic}と{\fnMS PGothic}“{\fnMS Gothic}蒼{\fnMS PGothic}”{\fnMS Gothic}
